      "definition_uri": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/attack/x_mitre_domains",
      "description": "The ATT&CK technology domains to which this object belongs. At least one domain must be specified. An object may belong to multiple domains when the same technique, group, or software is relevant across domain boundaries.",
      "comments": [
