      "definition_uri": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/stix/external_references",
      "description": "External references for this technique. The first entry MUST have source_name 'mitre-attack' with the ATT&CK ID as external_id (e.g., 'T1059' or 'T1059.001'). Additional entries may reference reports, malware analyses, or other sources.",
      "comments": [
        "validator_hint: first-ref-must-be-mitre-attack-technique-id jsonschema_minItems: \"1\""
